reviewText: Very beautiful Sara St. James who does about 10 different videos on the dvd most of which are fully nude after she totally teases you. These are only her in the videos and I only had to pay $70 bucks because this is a collectors item. She has started a church and doesn't do videos anymore. She still has a website with very sexy videos and photos you can download..

Sara St. James is one of the stage names of the actress Jacqueline Nyahay.  In her early years, she worked for MacDaddy Entertainment, doing nude and semi-nude video skits while she attended acting classes.  She no longer does nude work, so here is your chance to see this talented young actress strut her stuff.  MacDaddy collected the best of the work she did for them, and included those skits and videos here, along with some candid narration by Sara herself.  If you're a fan of Jacqueline Lovell/Nyahay, don't miss this title.  She is truly a Star!
